        <div class="cc-tags">
          <span class="cat-tag">星曜排布</span>
          <span class="cat-tag">命宫身宫</span>
          <span class="cat-tag">四化星</span>
          <span class="cat-tag">十二宫</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cat-card meihua" onclick="showSection('meihua')">
        <span class="cc-symbol">🌸</span>
        <span class="cc-name">梅花易数</span>
        <span class="cc-en">Meihua Yishu · Number Divination</span>
        <p class="cc-desc">以数起卦，体用分阴阳，五行生克论吉凶，简单而神妙</p>
        <div class="cc-tags">
          <span class="cat-tag">数字起卦</span>
          <span class="cat-tag">体用五行</span>
          <span class="cat-tag">万物类象</span>
          <span class="cat-tag">应期判断</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cat-card" style="border-color:rgba(230,126,34,.1)" onclick="showSection('liuren')">
        <span class="cc-symbol" style="color:#e67e22">⬡</span>
        <span class="cc-name" style="color:#e67e22">大六壬</span>
        <span class="cc-en">Da Liu Ren · Six Ren</span>
        <p class="cc-desc">六壬为三式之首，以天盘地盘人盘三传演万事，以神将断吉凶</p>
        <div class="cc-tags">
          <span class="cat-tag">三传四课</span>
          <span class="cat-tag">六神</span>
          <span class="cat-tag">五行神将</span>
          <span class="cat-tag">贵神课体</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== BAZI SECTION ===== -->
<section class="section" id="section-bazi">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="sh-symbol" style="color:var(--cyan)">🌟</span>
    <h2 class="sh-title">八字命盘</h2>
    <p class="sh-en">Four Pillars of Destiny</p>
    <p class="sh-desc">年柱映祖荫，月柱观父母，日干为本人，时柱知晚景。阴阳五行定命局，十神生克论人生。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="input-card">
    <h3>命主基本信息</h3>
    <div class="input-row">
      <input type="text" class="input-field" id="baziName" placeholder="姓名" maxlength="20">
      <input type="date" class="input-field" id="baziDate">
      <!-- 日历模式切换 -->
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px">
        <span style="font-size:12px;opacity:.5">历法</span>
        <label style="font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px">
          <input type="radio" name="calendarMode" value="solar" checked onchange="onCalendarModeChange()"> 公历
        </label>
        <label style="font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px">
          <input type="radio" name="calendarMode" value="lunar" onchange="onCalendarModeChange()"> 农历
        </label>
        <span id="calendarHint" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--gold);margin-left:4px">当前：公历输入</span>
      </div>
      <select class="input-field" id="baziHour" onchange="onShichenChange()">
        <option value="">时辰（选填）</option>
        <option value="23">子时 23:00-01:00（夜半）</option>
        <option value="1">丑时 01:00-03:00（鸡鸣）</option>
        <option value="3">寅时 03:00-05:00（平旦）</option>
        <option value="5">卯时 05:00-07:00（日出）</option>
        <option value="7">辰时 07:00-09:00（食时）</option>
        <option value="9">巳时 09:00-11:00（隅中）</option>
        <option value="11">午时 11:00-13:00（日中）</option>
        <option value="13">未时 13:00-15:00（日昳）</option>
        <option value="15">申时 15:00-17:00（晡时）</option>
        <option value="17">酉时 17:00-19:00（日入）</option>
        <option value="19">戌时 19:00-21:00（黄昏）</option>
        <option value="21">亥时 21:00-23:00（人定）</option>
      </select>
      <p class="input-hint" id="shichenHint">⚠️ 时辰按<b>农历</b>计算，每个时辰相当于2小时。以上时间对应农历时辰，公历时间仅作参考。</p>
      <p class="input-hint" style="cursor:pointer;color:var(--gold);font-size:11px" onclick="toggleShichenTable()">📋 时辰对照表（点击展开）</p>
      <!-- 时辰对照表（默认隐藏） -->
      <div id="shichenTable" style="display:none;margin-top:8px;padding:12px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.04);border-radius:8px;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8">
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:6px">
          <div style="padding:4px 8px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.08);border-radius:4px"><b>子时</b> 23:00-01:00<br><span style="opacity:.5">夜半·胆经当令</span></div>
          <div style="padding:4px 8px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.08);border-radius:4px"><b>丑时</b> 01:00-03:00<br><span style="opacity:.5">鸡鸣·肝经当令</span></div>
          <div style="padding:4px 8px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.08);border-radius:4px"><b>寅时</b> 03:00-05:00<br><span style="opacity:.5">平旦·肺经当令</span></div>
          <div style="padding:4px 8px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.08);border-radius:4px"><b>卯时</b> 05:00-07:00<br><span style="opacity:.5">日出·大肠经当令</span></div>
          <div style="padding:4px 8px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.08);border-radius:4px"><b>辰时</b> 07:00-09:00<br><span style="opacity:.5">食时·胃经当令</span></div>
          <div style="padding:4px 8px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.08);border-radius:4px"><b>巳时</b> 09:00-11:00<br><span style="opacity:.5">隅中·脾经当令</span></div>
          <div style="padding:4px 8px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.08);border-radius:4px"><b>午时</b> 11:00-13:00<br><span style="opacity:.5">日中·心经当令</span></div>
          <div style="padding:4px 8px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.08);border-radius:4px"><b>未时</b> 13:00-15:00<br><span style="opacity:.5">日昳·小肠经当令</span></div>
          <div style="padding:4px 8px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.08);border-radius:4px"><b>申时</b> 15:00-17:00<br><span style="opacity:.5">晡时·膀胱经当令</span></div>
          <div style="padding:4px 8px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.08);border-radius:4px"><b>酉时</b> 17:00-19:00<br><span style="opacity:.5">日入·肾经当令</span></div>
          <div style="padding:4px 8px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.08);border-radius:4px"><b>戌时</b> 19:00-21:00<br><span style="opacity:.5">黄昏·心包经当令</span></div>
          <div style="padding:4px 8px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.08);border-radius:4px"><b>亥时</b> 21:00-23:00<br><span style="opacity:.5">人定·三焦经当令</span></div>
        </div>
        <p style="margin-top:8px;opacity:.4;font-size:11px">注：农历以子时（23:00）为一日之始，与公历0:00为一日之始不同。排盘时请以出生地地方时为准。</p>
      </div>
      <select class="input-field" id="baziSex">
        <option value="male">男</option>
        <option value="female">女</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <p class="input-hint">出生日期为公历。时辰不填则按中午12:00计算。</p>
    <button class="compute-btn" onclick="computeBazi()" id="baziBtn">排 盘 演 命</button>
  </div>

  <div class="result" id="baziResult">
    <div class="result-banner">
      <h2 class="rb-name" id="baziNameOut"></h2>
      <p class="rb-meta" id="baziMetaOut"></p>
      <div class="rb-tags" id="baziTagsOut"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- PILLAR CHART -->
    <div class="pillar-chart">
      <div class="pillar-header">
        <div class="ph-col">年柱</div>
        <div class="ph-col">月柱</div>
        <div class="ph-col">日柱</div>
        <div class="ph-col">时柱</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-row">
        <div class="pr-col">
          <p class="pr-label">天干 · 地支</p>
          <p class="pr-gan gan-甲" id="bz0g"></p>
          <p class="pr-zhi zhi-子" id="bz0z"></p>
          <p class="pr-ele" id="bz0e"></p>
          <p class="pr-na" id="bz0n"></p>
        </div>
        <div class="pr-col">
          <p class="pr-label">天干 · 地支</p>
          <p class="pr-gan gan-甲" id="bz1g"></p>
          <p class="pr-zhi zhi-子" id="bz1z"></p>
          <p class="pr-ele" id="bz1e"></p>
          <p class="pr-na" id="bz1n"></p>
        </div>
        <div class="pr-col">
          <p class="pr-label">天干 · 地支</p>
          <p class="pr-gan gan-甲" id="bz2g"></p>
          <p class="pr-zhi zhi-子" id="bz2z"></p>
          <p class="pr-ele" id="bz2e"></p>
          <p class="pr-na" id="bz2n"></p>
        </div>
        <div class="pr-col">
          <p class="pr-label">天干 · 地支</p>
          <p class="pr-gan gan-甲" id="bz3g"></p>
          <p class="pr-zhi zhi-子" id="bz3z"></p>
          <p class="pr-ele" id="bz3e"></p>
          <p class="pr-na" id="bz3n"></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ANALYSIS -->
    <div class="analysis-grid" id="baziAnalysisGrid"></div>

    <!-- FIVE ELEMENTS BAR -->
    <div class="analysis-card" style="margin-bottom:16px">
      <h5>五行力量分布</h5>
      <div class="ele-bar" id="eleBar"></div>
      <div class="ele-legend" id="eleLegend"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- DAY MASTER TEN GODS -->
    <div class="analysis-card" style="margin-bottom:16px" id="tenGodsCard">
      <h5>日主十神 · 命格</h5>
      <div class="ten-gods-grid" id="tenGodsGrid"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- NAYIN FIVE ELEMENTS -->
    <div class="analysis-card" style="margin-top:24px">
      <h5 style="font-size:13px;letter-spacing:4px;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:12px">📜 纳音五行 · 六十甲子</h5>
      <div class="shensha-grid" id="nayinGrid"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- SHENSHA -->
    <div class="analysis-card" style="margin-top:24px">
      <h5 style="font-size:13px;letter-spacing:4px;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:12px">⭐ 神煞分析</h5>
      <div class="shensha-grid" id="shenshaGrid"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- GEJU -->
    <div class="huajie-alert" style="margin-top:20px" id="gejuBox">
      <div class="alert-title">命局分析</div>
      <p>格局：<strong id="gejuName"></strong></p>
      <p style="margin-top:8px" id="gejuDesc"></p>
    </div>

    <!-- HE CHONG -->
    <div class="analysis-card" style="margin-top:20px">
      <h5 style="font-size:13px;letter-spacing:4px;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:12px">🔗 合冲刑害</h5>
      <div class="shensha-grid" id="hechongGrid"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- 大运流年（专业升级版） -->
    <div class="analysis-card" style="margin-bottom:16px" id="dayunCard">
      <h5 style="font-size:15px;letter-spacing:4px;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px">
        🔮 大运流年 · 十年一运
        <span style="font-size:11px;opacity:.5;letter-spacing:1px;font-weight:normal">（起运年龄：<span id="qiyunAgeOut"></span>岁）</span>
      </h5>
      <!-- 大运时间轴 -->
      <div id="dayunTimeline" style="position:relative;padding:20px 0;margin-bottom:20px">
        <div id="dayunList" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:12px"></div>
      </div>
      <!-- 大运详细解读（点击展开） -->
      <div id="dayunDetail" style="display:none;margin-top:16px;padding:20px;background:rgba(201,168,76,.04);border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.1)">
        <h6 style="color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:12px" id="dayunDetailTitle"></h6>
        <div id="dayunDetailContent"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 命格深度解读 -->
    <div id="baziDimensionBox"></div>

    <div class="back-row">
      <button class="export-btn" onclick="exportBaziReport()">📋 导出命盘报告</button>
      <button class="back-btn" onclick="showSection('hero')">返 回 首 页</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== YIJING SECTION ===== -->
<section class="section" id="section-yijing">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="sh-symbol" style="color:var(--gold)">䷀</span>
    <h2 class="sh-title">易经六爻</h2>
    <p class="sh-en">I Ching · Six Lines · 64 Hexagrams</p>
    <p class="sh-desc">一念至诚，三掷金钱，显象分明。本卦为本，变卦为变，动静之间，命运自现。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="input-card">
    <h3>人盘 · 命格分析　　事盘 · 时局判断</h3>
    <div class="input-row">
      <input type="text" class="input-field" id="yjName" placeholder="姓名（可选）" maxlength="20">
    </div>
    <div class="input-row" style="margin-top:12px;gap:12px;justify-content:center">
      <button class="compute-btn" onclick="yjStart('person')" id="yjBtnP">人　盘</button>
      <button class="compute-btn" onclick="yjStart('matter')" id="yjBtnM">事　盘</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="yjDivArea" style="display:none">
    <div class="input-card" style="text-align:center;padding:40px">
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:8px;font-size:16px">金 钱 课</h3>
      <p style="font-size:11px;opacity:.35;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:30px">一念至诚，三掷金钱，显象分明</p>
      <div class="coins-row">
        <div class="coin" id="yjC0">背</div>
        <div class="coin" id="yjC1">背</div>
        <div class="coin" id="yjC2">背</div>
      </div>
      <div class="line-dots">
        <div class="ldot" id="yjD0"></div>
        <div class="ldot" id="yjD1"></div>
        <div class="ldot" id="yjD2"></div>
        <div class="ldot" id="yjD3"></div>
        <div class="ldot" id="yjD4"></div>
        <div class="ldot" id="yjD5"></div>
      </div>
      <button class="compute-btn" onclick="yjCast()" id="yjCastBtn">掷 钱 问 卦</button>
      <p id="yjCount" style="margin-top:14px;font-size:11px;opacity:.35;letter-spacing:2px">第 1 / 6 爻</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="result" id="yjResult">
    <div class="result-banner">
      <p style="font-size:12px;letter-spacing:5px;color:var(--gold);opacity:.5;margin-bottom:12px" id="yjMeta"></p>
      <h2 class="rb-name" style="font-size:clamp(36px,7vw,56px)" id="yjTitle"></h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);font-style:italic;letter-spacing:3px" id="yjPinyin"></p>
    </div>

    <div class="hexagram-row">
      <div class="hg-card" id="yjPrimary">
        <p class="hg-label">本　卦</p>
        <p class="hg-symbol" id="yjSym1"></p>
        <div class="gua-lines" id="yjGua1"></div>
        <p class="hg-name" id="yjName1"></p>
        <p class="hg-pinyin" id="yjPy1"></p>
        <p class="hg-judgment" id="yjJud1"></p>
        <p class="hg-meaning" id="yjMean1"></p>
      </div>
      <div class="arrow-div">→</div>
      <div class="hg-card changed" id="yjChanged" style="display:none">
        <p class="hg-label">变　卦</p>
        <p class="hg-symbol" id="yjSym2"></p>
        <div class="gua-lines" id="yjGua2"></div>
        <p class="hg-name" id="yjName2"></p>
        <p class="hg-pinyin" id="yjPy2"></p>
        <p class="hg-judgment" id="yjJud2"></p>
        <p class="hg-meaning" id="yjMean2"></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="yjInterp"></div>

    <div id="yjReadingBox"></div>

    <div class="back-row">
      <button class="back-btn" onclick="yjReset()">重 新 起 卦</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

