            </div>
            <div class="plan-desc"><strong>布局：</strong>客厅朝南，主卧朝南，次卧朝北，厨房东北，卫生间西北</div>
            <div class="plan-tags">
              <span class="tag auspicious">💰 财位（正东）</span>
              <span class="tag auspicious">📚 文昌位（东南）</span>
            </div>
            <div class="plan-dimensions">
              <div class="dim-bar"><span class="dim-label">方正度</span><span class="dim-track"><span class="dim-fill" style="width:90%"></span></span><span class="dim-num">90</span></div>
              <div class="dim-bar"><span class="dim-label">采光</span><span class="dim-track"><span class="dim-fill" style="width:95%"></span></span><span class="dim-num">95</span></div>
